<del rend="strikethrough">ʒe<gap reason="illegible"/> vnd vns nıht lıeb wer daʒ das als <expan>v<ex>er</ex>durplich</expan> <expan>lige<ex>n</ex></expan> vn </del></ab></add>
<add><ab facs="#facs_74_r1l1">vnd vns niht lıeb wer </ab><ab facs="#facs_74_r1l2">daʒ das als gar ver </ab><ab facs="#facs_74_r1l3">durplich <expan>lige<ex>n</ex></expan> vnd </ab><ab facs="#facs_74_r1l4">wider in ſchuld <expan>valle<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab><ab facs="#facs_74_r1l5">ſolt / Darumb ſo </ab><ab facs="#facs_74_r1l6"><expan>getrawe<ex>n</ex></expan> wir <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab><ab facs="#facs_74_r1l7"><expan>ervvirdik<ex>eit</ex></expan> wol Jr </ab></add>
<del rend="strikethrough"> das man das pawet / darumb ſo </del> lat eʒ bey </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_74_r2l26">cʒweyn Jungen Schotten <expan>bleib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vnd ſchickt der 
<add><ab facs="#facs_74_r2l25">cʒu der ʒeit </ab></add> nıht mer </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_74_r2l27">darein / Das <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> wir v̈mb <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> <expan>ervvirdik<ex>eit</ex></expan>
